title: Initial implentation of font previewing
message:
Initial implentation of font previewing
- When user long clicks a listview item (specific font), the app will download the regular font style associated with the one they clicked on. Then it will create a new typeface out of this regular font, and finally create a dialog with a test sentence (containing all letters in the alphabet) that uses the typeface.

title: Improve logic for download detection
message:
Improve logic for download detection
For each downloaded font, decrease the value of an int initialized with 12. Once it reaches zero, meaning that all 12 fonts were downloaded, proceed with futher action. This stops the alertdialog from popping up 12 times for each completed download.

title: Create FontList activity
message:
Create FontList activity
This acitivity reads the fonts from a text file in assets, stores the data into an ArrayList, and a ListView loads based on this list. When user clicks on list item the string value is taken and passed through a method to remove any spaces. From here the font string value can be put into a generic url which will point to the location of the files for that specific font.
